<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Customer Issue Report</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        th,
        td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h2>Customer Issue Report</h2>

    <p>Hello Team,</p>

    <p>A customer has reported the following issue:</p>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Customer Name</th>
            <td>{{username}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Email</th>
            <td>{{useremail}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Mobile Number</th>
            <td>{{usermo}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Issue Description</th>
            <td>{{feedback}}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <p>Please review and take appropriate action to address the customer's concern as soon as possible.</p>

    <p>Thank you.</p>
</body>

</html>